//   → resolve() returns [] + one W_TOPOLOGY_TAG_STALE diagnostic (Named interim
//     arm pushes one TopologyTagStale and returns an empty vec).
//
// "nope" matches no feature tag on the box, which is the expected interim
// behaviour (D8) during the v0.1→v0.2 migration window.
